description: Police say they are investigating a crime in the city of Solingen and the mother is a suspect.
title: Germany children deaths: Bodies of five found in flat in Solingen

maintext: "Background and further details are not known at this point and that is what we are trying to find out," Mr Weiand told journalists, adding that police investigators were at the scene "in full force".
